SUMMARY:July 4th Boat Parade
LOCATION:333 S. Franklin St Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:This year\, Friends of the Riverwalk is proud to host the annu
 al July 4th Boat Parade. Join the patriotic fun by decorating your boat an
 d cruising alongside fellow participants in this festive waterfront tradit
 ion. Boat registration is required to participate\, and this years special
  registration price is just 20.26 in honor of Americas upcoming semiquince
 ntennial birthday celebration! Boat Registration is now open! Register you
 r boat for 20.26 in honor of 2026 and Americas 250th celebration! Registra
 tion is required to participate in the boat parade. Registration includes:
  Invitation to Captains Party Boater Swag Bag Registration Numbers Registe
 red Boater Pennant Flag Fireworks Viewing Chance to Win Most Patriotic Tro
 phy Chance to Win Other Prizes \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/1
 91781
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/191781
END:VEVENT
