LOCATION:801 Water Street Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:Enjoy a guided tour of America at the Crossroads: The GUITAR a
 nd a Changing Nation and explore Americas evolution through the lens of it
 s most popular instrument. Discover how the guitar has reflected generatio
 nal change\, racial division\, politics\, consumer culture\, and shifting 
 trends throughout the nations history. Registration is free but required: 
 https:13509.blackbaudhosting.com13509Archives-Awareness-Week-Guitars-and-G
