DESCRIPTION:The Youth and Young Adult Wellness Summit is a community-cente
 red event hosted by NAMI Hillsborough focused on promoting mental wellness
 \, emotional health\, and access to community resources for youth\, young 
 adults\, and families throughout the Tampa Bay area. The summit will featu
 re wellness discussions\, community resources\, youth engagement activitie
 s\, inspirational speakers\, and educational sessions designed to reduce s
 tigma and encourage healthy conversations around mental health and overall
  well-being. The event will take place on July 18\, 2026\, at the Universi
 ty of South Florida. Complimentary continental breakfast and lunch will be
