SUMMARY:Laser Light Shows: Country U2
LOCATION:4801 E Fowler Ave. Tampa \, FL 33617 United States
DESCRIPTION:Laser Light Shows are taking over the Holloway Digital Dome Th
 eatre\, home to the Saunders Planetarium. Step inside Americas second-larg
 est planetarium and experience vivid laser visuals\, dynamic music\, and d
 azzling special effects. Designed for all ages\, our Laser Light Shows hav
 e something for everyone. Each performance pairs stunning visuals with you
 r favorite soundtracks. You wont just watch the show\, youll feel like you
 re part of it. Before the lasers hit the dome\, our astronomer will guide 
 you through a live star show\, taking you on a journey into the night sky.
  Dont miss this exciting mix of science\, music\, and light at MOSI! Wheth
 er youre a first-timer or a longtime fan\, youll be amazed. Tickets are li
 mited\, snag yours today before they sell out! \n\nPermalink: https://www.
 tampa.gov/node/192541
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/192541
END:VEVENT
