SUMMARY:Through Their Lens: A Journey of Self-Exploration Opening Receptio
 n
LOCATION:1630 E. 7th Ave. Tampa \, FL 33605 United States
DESCRIPTION:The Florida Museum of Photographic Arts is proud to present Th
 rough Their Lens: A Journey of Self-Exploration\, a compelling exhibition 
 featuring the work of emerging student photographers from across the Tampa
  Bay area. On view August 4 through September 20\, 2026\, the exhibition h
 ighlights the creativity\, perspective\, and personal storytelling of youn
 g artists exploring identity\, environment\, and self-expression through p
 hotography. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/192066
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/192066
