SUMMARY:Downtowns Backyard Market
LOCATION:200 N. Franklin Street Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:Find fresh finds and city vibes at Downtowns Backyard Market! 
 This monthly market invites you to Tampa City Centers Esplanade (Poe Plaza
 ) to get down to earth as local businesses and vendors bring fresh produce
  and food to the heart of Downtown. From petals to pastries\, this is your
  chance to discover an abundance of local flavors in the city center. Join
  us the second Thursday of each month to explore a rotating lineup of loca
