SUMMARY:Art Aces: A Night of Vintage Glamour
LOCATION:120 W. Gasparilla Plaza Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:Art Aces celebrates its 4th anniversary and invites you to ste
 p into the glamour and sophistication of the Art Deco era. Sponsors and gu
 ests can expect an unforgettable evening where vintage glamour is the dres
 s code\, and generosity is the highest stake at the table. This unforgetta
 ble evening will feature classic casino games\, lively entertainment\, and
  an atmosphere of vintage grandeur. Step into a world of elegance\, perfec
 tly poured cocktails and mocktails\, amazing cuisine\, and the timeless th
 rill of the game\, all set against the stunning backdrop of one of Florida
 s most celebrated cultural institutions. This is a night for Tampa Bays fi
 nest  where the roulette wheel spins\, dice roll\, masterpieces adorn the 
 walls\, and every hand played writes the next chapter of our citys artisti
 c legacy. Open bar  DJ  gaming tables  hors Doeuvres Dress to impress. Pla
 y to win. Give to inspire. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/19258
 6
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/192586
END:VEVENT
